body_html: On the computer of a colleague we installed tensorflow 1.12 from scratch and my code runs successfully indeed. It is a machine with Windows 10, but with different Nvidia gpu (Quadro K610M). I'll do a more thorough reinstall of the tensorflow dependency chain on my machine and will let you know.
